        }

**NOTE**: This program uses `Character.getNumericValue` - be careful using this  as it may not always work as you may expect (specially for non numeric values). Make sure to read the documentation [here](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/lang/Character.html#getNumericValue(char))

