the `@Database` annotation is changed to:-

    @Database( entities = {User.class,Meeting.class,UserMeetingMap.class}, exportSchema = false, version = 1)

After compiling then the Room v Original SQL is:-

    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `UserMeetingMap` (`usermap` INTEGER NOT NULL, `meetingmap` INTEGER NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`usermap`, `meetingmap`), FOREIGN KEY(`usermap`) REFERENCES `User`(`userid`) ON UPDATE CASCADE ON DELETE CASCADE , FOREIGN KEY(`meetingmap`) REFERENCES `Meeting`(`meetingid`) ON UPDATE CASCADE ON DELETE CASCADE )

