2. in `Sum` threads you don&#39;t wait for `arr[i-1]` and `arr[i+1]` to get computed before computing `arr[i]`.  
  Don&#39;t forget that `Sum.run()` are executed in parallel (because they are executed in different threads), and when some thread computes `a[i]`, then there are no guarantees that the other threads have just computed the right iterations of `a[i-1]` and `a[i+1]`.

